Dialogue: 7,0:19:08.00,0:19:12.11,Insert_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fax-0.15\blur4}僕にそっと触れてみて
Dialogue: 7,0:19:12.51,0:19:18.45,Insert_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fax-0.15\blur4}この心はキミのもの
